OL,4,CSenior MP demands answers for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,6, MP Clive Betts has written to the
OL,7, government to ask why new guidance
OL,8, designed to help about 500,000
OL,9, leaseholders sell or remortgage their
OL,10, flats is not being followed.
OL,12,FIt was issued by the Royal Institution
OL,13,Fof Chartered Surveyors (RICS) in March.
OL,15,FIt is supposed to help surveyors decide
OL,16,Fwhich tower blocks need extra fire
OL,17,Fsafety checks.
OL,19,FBut although mortgage providers were
OL,20,Fconsulted on the guidance, Money Box
OL,21,Fhas found some lenders are ignoring it.
